{"about_the_game":"<strong>Futuristic Museum</strong> is a virtual reality museum where you can see and experience future museums with various themes. Try various experiences at home, such as mysterious and beautiful spaces, and exhibits you can touch!<br><br><strong>Futuristic Museum</strong> consists of a lobby and three exhibitions related to each subject. Each exhibit is a mineral, an aquarium, and a statue.<br><br><strong>Lobby</strong><br>* In the lobby, there are tutorials on how to operate and a portal to each exhibition.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946530/extras/Main.png?t=1652526687\" /><br><br><strong>Mineral exhibition</strong><br>* In the mineral exhibition hall, you can see and touch various minerals.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946530/extras/Mineral.png?t=1652526687\" /><br><br><strong>Aquarium</strong><br>* In the aquarium, you can see aquatic creatures and play rock climbing mini-games.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946530/extras/Aquarium.png?t=1652526687\" /><br><br><strong>Statue exhibition</strong><br>* In the statue exhibition hall, you can see and touch information about oriental statues.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946530/extras/Animal.png?t=1652526687\" /><br><br><strong>Info</strong><br>* You can view information about the exhibits by clicking the information button next to each exhibition stand.<br>* By pressing the button on your wrist, you can open the mini-map of the current exhibition hall and a menu that allows you to move to the desired place.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946530/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1652526687","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/194